 <br/><a name='toc_1'></a>
<h1 class='doclevel'>1.Test Suite : hair3540_WBT</h1>
<div><p>Se testează calculul totalului unei comenzi</p>
</div><a name="toc_tc29257"></a><p>&nbsp;</p><div> <table class="tc" width="90%" ><tr><th colspan="4">Test Case P233-56: CalculareTotalComandăTestcase1&nbsp;<span style="font-size: 80%;">[Version  : 1]</span></th></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Author:</span></td><td colspan="3">icir3549</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan="4"><span class="label">Summary:</span><br /><p>Se calculează total unei comenzi care conține:</p>

<ul>
	<li>apă (produs valid și existent &icirc;n stoc), 2 bucăți</li>
	<li>cafea (produs valid și existent &icirc;n stoc), 1 bucată</li>
</ul>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p>Totalul calculat trebuie să fie egal cu: &euro;_apă * 2 + &euro;_cafea</p>
</td></tr><tr><td colspan="4"><span class="label">Preconditions:</span><br /><ul>
	<li>o: Order</li>
	<li>o != null</li>
	<li>o.getItems() == [<br />
	&nbsp; OrderItem(Produs(&#39;Apa&#39;, 14), 2)<br />
	&nbsp; OrderItem(Produs(&#39;Cafea&#39;, 16), 1)<br />
	]</li>
	<li>&exist; Produs(&#39;Apa&#39;)</li>
	<li>&exist; Produs(&#39;Cafea&#39;)</li>
</ul>
</td></tr><tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Execution type:</span></td><td colspan="3">Manual</td></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Estimated exec. duration (min):</span></td><td colspan="3"></td></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Importance:</span></td><td colspan="3">Medium</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan="4"></td></tr><tr><td > name of the autotest class:</td><td  colspan = "3" >drinkshop.service.CalculateTotalOrderTest</td></tr>
<tr><td > name of the test method:</td><td  colspan = "3" >drinkshop.service.CalculateTotalOrderTest#calculateTotalOrderTotal_Valid</td></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Requirements</span><td colspan="3">hair3540_F02:  SpecificareCalculareTotalComandă [Version : 1]<br /></td></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Keywords:</span></td><td colspan="3">&nbsp;None<br/></td></tr>
</table>
</div>
<a name="toc_tc29259"></a><p>&nbsp;</p><div> <table class="tc" width="90%" ><tr><th colspan="4">Test Case P233-57: CalculareTotalComandăTestcase2&nbsp;<span style="font-size: 80%;">[Version  : 1]</span></th></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Author:</span></td><td colspan="3">icir3549</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan="4"><span class="label">Summary:</span><br /><p>Se calculează total unei comenzi care conține:</p>

<ul>
	<li>apă (produs valid și existent &icirc;n stoc), 2 bucăți</li>
	<li>lapte (produs valid și existent &icirc;n stoc), 0 bucăți</li>
	<li>ceai (produs valid și existent &icirc;n stoc), 1 bucată</li>
</ul>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p>Trebuie să fie returnată o excepție din cauza produsului lapte care are o cantitate vidă</p>
</td></tr><tr><td colspan="4"><span class="label">Preconditions:</span><br /><ul>
	<li>o: Order</li>
	<li>o != null</li>
	<li>o.getItems() == [<br />
	&nbsp; OrderItem(Produs(&#39;Apa&#39;, 14), 2),<br />
	&nbsp; OrderItem(Produs(&#39;Lapte&#39;, 16), 0),<br />
	&nbsp; OrderItem(Produs(&#39;Ceai&#39;, 10), 1),<br />
	]</li>
	<li>&exist; Produs(&#39;Apa&#39;)</li>
	<li>&exist; Produs(&#39;Lapte&#39;)</li>
	<li>&exist; Produs(&#39;Ceai&#39;)</li>
</ul>
</td></tr><tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Execution type:</span></td><td colspan="3">Manual</td></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Estimated exec. duration (min):</span></td><td colspan="3"></td></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Importance:</span></td><td colspan="3">Medium</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan="4"></td></tr><tr><td > name of the autotest class:</td><td  colspan = "3" >drinkshop.service.CalculateTotalOrderTest</td></tr>
<tr><td > name of the test method:</td><td  colspan = "3" >drinkshop.service.CalculateTotalOrderTest#calculateTotalOrderTotal_Invalid</td></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Requirements</span><td colspan="3">hair3540_F02:  SpecificareCalculareTotalComandă [Version : 1]<br /></td></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Keywords:</span></td><td colspan="3">&nbsp;None<br/></td></tr>
</table>
