<a name="toc_tc29371"></a><p>&nbsp;</p><div> <table class="tc" width="90%" ><tr><th colspan="4">Test Case P233-62: CalculateTotalComandaTestcase3&nbsp;<span style="font-size: 80%;">[Version  : 1]</span></th></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Author:</span></td><td colspan="3">icir3549</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan="4"><span class="label">Summary:</span><br /><p>Se calculează total unei comenzi care conține:</p>

